Detailed Description

A base pair info structure.

For each base pair (i,j) with i,j in [0, n-1] the structure lists:

  • its probability 'p'
  • an entropy-like measure for its well-definedness 'ent'
  • the frequency of each type of pair in 'bp[]' + 'bp[0]' contains the number of non-compatible sequences + 'bp[1]' the number of CG pairs, etc.
